  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: d6fced335fe0e624e8c9d175d9ff6239, type: 3}
  m_Name: GoddessIntroDialogue
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::DialogueData
  startNodeIndex: 0
  nodes:
  - editorLabel: Intro - Aria Unknown
    lines:
    - speaker: ???
      text: ...Oh? I thought I had sent everyone. What an annoying turn of events.
      portraitOverride: {fileID: -8624218529645720774, guid: bd0fcb775d3be024693002dc2d62ed16, type: 3}
      emote: 
      sfx: {fileID: 0}
      sfxVolume: 1
      autoAdvanceDelay: 0
      tags: []
    - speaker: ???
      text: Casting that spell again will be quite tiresome.. but perhaps you'll
        be worth the hassle.
      portraitOverride: {fileID: 4550699245769742691, guid: 21ac720a564f81049a22753b44270c65, type: 3}
      emote: 
      sfx: {fileID: 0}
      sfxVolume: 1
      autoAdvanceDelay: 0
      tags: []
    - speaker: ???
      text: Let's check your aptitude...
      portraitOverride: {fileID: -8624218529645720774, guid: bd0fcb775d3be024693002dc2d62ed16, type: 3}
      emote: 
      sfx: {fileID: 0}
      sfxVolume: 1
      autoAdvanceDelay: 1
      tags: []
    - speaker: ???
      text: ...
      portraitOverride: {fileID: 7915047514232459791, guid: 446a7bb644a08064fb498bbefbecf419, type: 3}
      emote: 
      sfx: {fileID: 0}
      sfxVolume: 1
      autoAdvanceDelay: 1.5
      tags:
      - flash
    - speaker: ???
      text: You.
      portraitOverride: {fileID: 7915047514232459791, guid: 446a7bb644a08064fb498bbefbecf419, type: 3}
      emote: 
      sfx: {fileID: 0}
      sfxVolume: 1
      autoAdvanceDelay: 1
      tags: []
    - speaker: ???
      text: ...are the most unremarkable soul I have ever seen.
      portraitOverride: {fileID: 21300000, guid: bcc177860d7e67d4384e830a84bd222a, type: 3}
      emote: 
      sfx: {fileID: 0}
      sfxVolume: 1
      autoAdvanceDelay: 0
      tags: []
    - speaker: ???
      text: What can I even do with such garbage?
      portraitOverride: {fileID: 21300000, guid: bcc177860d7e67d4384e830a84bd222a, type: 3}
      emote: 
      sfx: {fileID: 0}
      sfxVolume: 1
      autoAdvanceDelay: 0
      tags: []
    choices: []
    nextNodeIndex: 1
  - editorLabel: Lucien Interjects
    lines:
    - speaker: ????
      text: Aria, Goddess, if I may...
      portraitOverride: {fileID: -4167606202100583031, guid: 9053ac42e58f5704cbd1a3f3e07567f5, type: 3}
      emote: 
      sfx: {fileID: 0}
      sfxVolume: 1
      autoAdvanceDelay: 0
      tags: []
    - speaker: ????
      text: Perhaps you can send them over to eastern Alma. That continent is usually
        neglected by heroes.
      portraitOverride: {fileID: -2181019024026239553, guid: d6f317a2b0305e14abd20b3d02a53cce, type: 3}
      emote: 
      sfx: {fileID: 0}
      sfxVolume: 1
      autoAdvanceDelay: 0
      tags: []
    choices: []
    nextNodeIndex: 2
  - editorLabel: Aria Decides
    lines:
    - speaker: Goddess Aria
      text: The eastern continent... yes, that could work.
      portraitOverride: {fileID: 4550699245769742691, guid: 21ac720a564f81049a22753b44270c65, type: 3}
      emote: 
      sfx: {fileID: 0}
      sfxVolume: 1
      autoAdvanceDelay: 0
      tags: []
    - speaker: Goddess Aria
      text: Whether they survive or not, it will still be beneficial for me.
      portraitOverride: {fileID: 4550699245769742691, guid: 21ac720a564f81049a22753b44270c65, type: 3}
      emote: 
      sfx: {fileID: 0}
      sfxVolume: 1
      autoAdvanceDelay: 0
      tags: []
    - speaker: Goddess Aria
      text: I suppose you're good for some things, Lucien.
      portraitOverride: {fileID: 4550699245769742691, guid: 21ac720a564f81049a22753b44270c65, type: 3}
      emote: 
      sfx: {fileID: 0}
      sfxVolume: 1
      autoAdvanceDelay: 0
      tags: []
    choices: []
    nextNodeIndex: 3
  - editorLabel: Lucien Thanks + Player Choice
    lines:
    - speaker: Lucien
      text: Thank you, my lady.
      portraitOverride: {fileID: 7223458760992213041, guid: c1d3de320eeb2984989a618198382e64, type: 3}
      emote: 
      sfx: {fileID: 0}
      sfxVolume: 1
      autoAdvanceDelay: 0
      tags: []
    choices:
    - choiceText: (Don't I get a say in this?)
      nextNodeIndex: 4
    - choiceText: (...)
      nextNodeIndex: 5
    nextNodeIndex: -1
  - editorLabel: Aria Humors Player
    lines:
    - speaker: Goddess Aria
      text: No, but I'll allow *1* question.
      portraitOverride: {fileID: -8624218529645720774, guid: bd0fcb775d3be024693002dc2d62ed16, type: 3}
      emote: 
      sfx: {fileID: 0}
      sfxVolume: 1
      autoAdvanceDelay: 0
      tags: []
    choices:
    - choiceText: (Can't you just send me back?)
      nextNodeIndex: 6
    - choiceText: (I don't understand what's happening, can you at least tell me?)
      nextNodeIndex: 7
    - choiceText: (Where are we?)
      nextNodeIndex: 8
    nextNodeIndex: -1
  - editorLabel: Silent Dismissal
    lines:
    - speaker: Goddess Aria
      text: Off you go.
      portraitOverride: {fileID: 4550699245769742691, guid: 21ac720a564f81049a22753b44270c65, type: 3}
      emote: 
      sfx: {fileID: 0}
      sfxVolume: 1
      autoAdvanceDelay: 0
      tags:
      - teleport
      - end_cutscene
    choices: []
    nextNodeIndex: -1
  - editorLabel: Send Me Back
    lines:
    - speaker: Goddess Aria
      text: Oh, I could, but where you end up... and how, will be entirely up to
        your luck.
      portraitOverride: {fileID: -8624218529645720774, guid: bd0fcb775d3be024693002dc2d62ed16, type: 3}
      emote: 
      sfx: {fileID: 0}
      sfxVolume: 1
      autoAdvanceDelay: 0
      tags: []
    - speaker: Goddess Aria
      text: It is far easier to send a wide range signal and wait for someone to
        bite, than it is to safely transport your body across space, to a far away
        place out of my influence.
      portraitOverride: {fileID: -8624218529645720774, guid: bd0fcb775d3be024693002dc2d62ed16, type: 3}
      emote: 
      sfx: {fileID: 0}
      sfxVolume: 1
      autoAdvanceDelay: 0
      tags: []
    - speaker: Goddess Aria
      text: You can blame your local gods, they're annoying to deal with.
      portraitOverride: {fileID: 21300000, guid: bcc177860d7e67d4384e830a84bd222a, type: 3}
      emote: 
      sfx: {fileID: 0}
      sfxVolume: 1
      autoAdvanceDelay: 0
      tags: []
    - speaker: Goddess Aria
      text: But that's enough of that, off you go then.
      portraitOverride: {fileID: 4550699245769742691, guid: 21ac720a564f81049a22753b44270c65, type: 3}
      emote: 
      sfx: {fileID: 0}
      sfxVolume: 1
      autoAdvanceDelay: 0
      tags:
      - teleport
      - end_cutscene
    choices: []
    nextNodeIndex: -1
  - editorLabel: Explain - Lore Dump
    lines:
    - speaker: Goddess Aria
      text: It's quite simple really, I intended to summon 5 heroes, casting a wide
        range sonar spell. You happened to respond.
      portraitOverride: {fileID: -8624218529645720774, guid: bd0fcb775d3be024693002dc2d62ed16, type: 3}
      emote: 
      sfx: {fileID: 0}
      sfxVolume: 1
      autoAdvanceDelay: 0
      tags: []
    - speaker: Goddess Aria
      text: Of course, you may not remember, but you must have answered 'yes' when
        I asked if you wished to become a 'hero'.
      portraitOverride: {fileID: 21300000, guid: bcc177860d7e67d4384e830a84bd222a, type: 3}
      emote: 
      sfx: {fileID: 0}
      sfxVolume: 1
      autoAdvanceDelay: 0
      tags: []
    - speaker: Goddess Aria
      text: As for why you appeared so late... I am not sure, but the heroes have
        already been chosen.
      portraitOverride: {fileID: -8624218529645720774, guid: bd0fcb775d3be024693002dc2d62ed16, type: 3}
      emote: 
      sfx: {fileID: 0}
      sfxVolume: 1
      autoAdvanceDelay: 0
      tags: []
    - speaker: Goddess Aria
      text: You are nothing but an extra, unneeded, talentless, nuisance.
      portraitOverride: {fileID: -8624218529645720774, guid: bd0fcb775d3be024693002dc2d62ed16, type: 3}
      emote: 
      sfx: {fileID: 0}
      sfxVolume: 1
      autoAdvanceDelay: 0
      tags: []
    - speaker: Goddess Aria
      text: It's a shame that I cannot dispose of you directly, perhaps your existence
        would serve some meaning then...
      portraitOverride: {fileID: 4550699245769742691, guid: 21ac720a564f81049a22753b44270c65, type: 3}
      emote: 
      sfx: {fileID: 0}
      sfxVolume: 1
      autoAdvanceDelay: 0
      tags: []
    - speaker: Goddess Aria
      text: Well, 'hero', it's time for you to face the world, may we never see each
        other again.
      portraitOverride: {fileID: 4550699245769742691, guid: 21ac720a564f81049a22753b44270c65, type: 3}
      emote: 
      sfx: {fileID: 0}
      sfxVolume: 1
      autoAdvanceDelay: 0
      tags:
      - teleport
      - end_cutscene
    choices: []
    nextNodeIndex: -1
  - editorLabel: Where Are We
    lines:
    - speaker: Goddess Aria
      text: My home. This will be the last time you lay eyes upon it.
      portraitOverride: {fileID: -8624218529645720774, guid: bd0fcb775d3be024693002dc2d62ed16, type: 3}
      emote: 
      sfx: {fileID: 0}
      sfxVolume: 1
      autoAdvanceDelay: 0
      tags: []
    - speaker: Goddess Aria
      text: Normally I'd play nice, but this whole thing has been a bore.
      portraitOverride: {fileID: 21300000, guid: bcc177860d7e67d4384e830a84bd222a, type: 3}
      emote: 
      sfx: {fileID: 0}
      sfxVolume: 1
      autoAdvanceDelay: 0
      tags: []
    - speaker: Goddess Aria
      text: Off you go.
      portraitOverride: {fileID: 4550699245769742691, guid: 21ac720a564f81049a22753b44270c65, type: 3}
      emote: 
      sfx: {fileID: 0}
      sfxVolume: 1
      autoAdvanceDelay: 0
      tags:
      - teleport
      - end_cutscene
    choices: []
    nextNodeIndex: -1
